Package com.dff.cordova.plugin.location.plugin.action

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeleteLocations
    Action to delete locations filtered by jsonArgs.
    DeleteLocationUpdateRequest
    Action to delete a specific location update request.
    DeleteProximityAlert
    Action to delete a specific proximity alert.
    DeleteProximityAlertEvents
    Action to delete proximity alert events filtered by parameters.
    GetAllProviders
    Action that returns all available location providers.
    GetConfig
    Action to get current configuration.
    GetLastKnownLocation
    Returns a location indicating the data from the last known location fix obtained from the given provider.
    GetLocations
    Action that returns locations filtered by given arguments.
    GetLocationUpdateRequests
    Action that returns a map of all known location update requests.
    GetProvider
    Action that returns a provider based on given provider name.
    GetProximityAlertEvents
    Returns a array of proximity alert events filtered by given parameters.
    GetProximityAlerts
    Action that returns a map of all known proximity alerts.
    IsLocationEnabled
    Action to get current enabled/disabled state of location mode.
    IsProviderEnabled
    Action that checks if the given provider is enabled.
    LocationAction
    Abstract class to classify location actions.
    OnLocationStatusChanged
    Action to listen to location mode changes.
    OnLocationUpdate
    Action to listen to location updates.
    OnProviderEnabled
    Action to listen to mode changes of the location providers.
    OnProximityAlert
    Action to listen to proximity alerts.
    Pause
    Action to pause location updates and proximity alerts.
    ReadDiagnostics
    Action to read diagnostics.
    RequestLocationUpdate
    Action to request location updates for given criteria or provider.
    RequestProximityAlert
    Action to request proximity alert for given arguments.
    Resume
    Action to resume location updates and proximity alerts.
    SetConfig
    Action to set config for location component.
    StartForeground
    Action to start foreground service with notifcation to keep on receiving location updates.
    StopForeground
    Action to stop the foreground service.
